prospective Financial Representatives. Focus of calls will 
frequently be to mid and low level producers in remote locations 
that the field sales force is unable to visit to facilitate full sales 
territory coverage. Plans, writes and prepares sales presentations 
for use with Financial Representatives.

<BR><BR>

Approximately two to three years of financial sales or customer 
service work experience necessary. Series 7 (General Securities 
Registered Rep) and Series 63 (Blue Sky) licenses, as well as 
Insurance licenses are desirable.

