is 5.0% for Kemper Retirement Fund.  Sales charges are reduced or eliminated under
certain conditions as described in the funds' prospectuses.
</FONT>

<P>

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="../gifs/whizdom_iconlarge.gif"> 

<STRONG>
<A HREF="fundsvsindices.html">
Compare Your Fund Against A Broad Market Index</A>
</STRONG>

