<P>
<B><FONT SIZE=4><I>The mission of the Internet Privacy Coalition is to promote
 privacy and security on the Internet through widespread public availability of strong encryption and the relaxation of export controls on cryptography.</I></FONT><BR></b>
<P>
<CENTER>
Last modified: February 3, 1997<BR>
