<FONT SIZE=4><I>"The multiple human needs and desires that demand privacy among
 two 
or more people in the midst of social life must inevitably lead to cryptology
wherever men thrive and wherever they write."</I><P>
-- David Kahn, The Codebreakers<BR>
</FONT>

