<TITLE>PRIVACY INTERNATIONAL - Country Reports</TITLE> 
<center><img align=bottom src="http://www.privacy.org/pi/PI.gif" hspace=4 vspace=4 height=85 width=85>

<H1>Country Reports</H1>
</center>




<p><br><br>
<H2>General Materials</H2>
<ul>

<li><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.privacy.org/pi/reports/hr95_privacy_report.html">1995 Review of International Privacy Rights</A>: Excerpts from the US State Department's "Country Reports on Human Rights for 1995. Privacy International's <!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.privacy.org/pi/reports/1995_hranalysis.html">analysis</A> of the report.<p>


<li><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.privacy.org/pi/reports/state_dept.html">1994 Review of International Privacy:</A> Excerpts from the US State Department's "Country Reports on Human Rights for 1994."<p>

<li><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.privacy.org/pi/reports/interim_report_1991.html">1991 Interim Report</A> to Members. Includes country reports and history of Privacy International.<p>


</ul>
<br>
