<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>PRIVACY AND THE CANADIAN INFORMATION HIGHWAY</H1>
<HR>
<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>REVIEW OF COMMENTS RECEIVED ON THE INDUSTRY CANADA DISCUSSION PAPER</H3>
<BR><BR>
<P ALIGN=CENTER>AKAY INFORMATION CONSULTING INC.<BR>
P.O. BOX 1268,  CARLETON PLACE<BR>
ONTARIO,  K7C 4L4<BR>
(613) 257-1072<BR>
March  1995</P>
<H3><A HREF="execsum.html">Executive Summary</A></H3>
<H3><A HREF="report.html">Full Report</A></H3>
<H3><A HREF="APPENDXA.TXT">Appendix A - Summary of Submissions</A></H3>
<H3><A HREF="APPENDXB.TXT">Appendix B - Canadian Standards Association Principles</A></H3>

</BODY>
