href="http://www.cpsr.org/cpsr/privacy/privacy_international/international_laws/international_covenant_social_economic_rights.txt"> International Covenant on Economic, Social and Cultural Rights</a>
</ul><BR>


<H3>UN Conventions</H3>
<ul>
<li><a 
href="http://www.cpsr.org/cpsr/privacy/privacy_international/international_laws/un_charter.txt"> Charter of the United Nations</a><P>

<li><a 
href="http://www.cpsr.org/cpsr/privacy/privacy_international/international_laws/intl_ct_justice_statute.txt">Statute of the International Court of Justice</a><P>

<li><a 
href="http://www.cpsr.org/cpsr/privacy/privacy_international/international_laws/un_conv_migrant_workers.txt">International Convention on the Protection of the Rights of All Migrant Workers and Members of Their Families</a><P>

<li><a 
href="http://www.cpsr.org/cpsr/privacy/privacy_international/international_laws/un_decl_draft_on_indigenous_persons.txt">Draft declaration on the rights of indigenous peoples</a><P>

<li><a 
href="http://www.cpsr.org/cpsr/privacy/privacy_international/international_laws/convention_against_torture.txt">Convention Against Torture</a><P>

<li><a 
href="http://www.cpsr.org/cpsr/privacy/privacy_international/international_laws/convention_rights_child.txt">Convention on the Rights of the Child</a><P>
</ul>
<hr size=4 >
<p>
