<li>Central Computer and Telecommunications Agency report, <!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.open.gov.uk./ccta/at/hottech/techagen/smartc/smartc.htm#The top">Smart cards: Opportunities for public sector applications</A>.<P> 

<li><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.cms.dmu.ac.uk/CCSR/ccsr/pubs/papers/id.html">The Green Paper on Identity Cards: A response from the Centre for Computing and Social Responsibility</A> by Simon Rogerson.<P>

<li>"<!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.wadham.ox.ac.uk/~rhouston/think/id-lib.html">Identity Crisis: why ID cards are a solution looking for a problem</A>" by Liz Parratt from Liberty.<p>

<li>"<!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.sbu.ac.uk/cop/idcards.html">IDENTITY CARDS: Data protection implications</A>" by Chris Pounder, Data Protection News (UK).<p>

