<DOCHDR>
http://www.privacy.org:80/pi/activities/idcard/campaigns.html 199.34.33.146 19970209033219 text/html 30739
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 09 Feb 1997 03:32:27 GMT
