<HEAD><TITLE>The European Union Directive on Data Protection</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"> 
<CENTER><H1>The European Union</H1></CENTER>

      <H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Directive 95/46/EC</H2>

<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>on the protection of individuals with regard to the
  processing of personal data and on the free movement of
                                   such data</H3>

<BR>
<BR>

<H3>
<A HREF="http://www.privacy.org/pi/intl_orgs/ec/dp_EC_press_release.txt">EU Press Release on Directive</A>  (July 25, 1995)</H3>

<li><h3>English</h3>
<ul>
<!-- Link Tag -->
<li><A HREF="http://www.privacy.org/pi/intl_orgs/ec/final_EU_Data_Protection.html">Local Text  Version (includes recitals)</A>. <p>

<li><A HREF="http://www2.echo.lu/legal/en/dataprot/directiv/directiv.html">HTML Version</A>. <p>

<li><A HREF="http://www2.echo.lu/legal/en/dataprot/directiv/recitals.html">HTML Recitals</A>

</ul>
<li><h3>French</h3>
<ul>
